                    <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 service">
                <i class="fa fa-area-chart"></i>
                <h4><strong>Crime Data</strong></h4>
                <p>We've worked with authorities across the globe to compile a comprehensive crime index by city. The data takes into account all types of crimes, including personal, property, and inchoate.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 service">
                <i class="fa fa-home"></i>
                <h4><strong>Safe House Mapper</strong></h4>
                <p>A tailored index of safe locations is generated for each trip you add to your itinerary. These locations include nearby banks, hospitals, airports and embassies. Additionally, a list of cafes, pharmacies and public transportation options is also populated.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 service">
                <i class="fa fa-bolt"></i>
                <h4><strong>Weather Tracking</strong></h4>
                <p>Using state of the art weather radars, Travel Aegis provides you with up to the moment weather data and any relevant weather alerts. Weather is monitored and updated at the push of a button.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 service">
                <i class="fa fa-warning"></i>
                <h4><strong>Risk Assessment</strong></h4>
                <p>By utilizing a complex algorithm, we create a custom risk assesment for your trip. The assesment takes into account the multitude of data sources Travel Aegis employs, including crime, safehouse locations, biological, metrological, climatological, geophysical and hydrological factors. Based on this number, we are able to provide you with an accurate snapshot of the risks that could threaten your safety.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
